\{helpitem -name _hu_flamethrower Flamethrower}
\{img /bunit:hu_flamethrower -ralign}
   \{tooltipshort}
%/class:chtr/vschtr:++/vsanml:+/vsvhcl:-/vsship:-/vsbldg:++%
   \{/tooltipshort}
   \{tooltipmedium}
• Infantry unit
\\{br}• Causes area damage
\\{br}• Damages enemy and neutral units
\\{br}• Can ignite buildings
\\{br}• Can use his weapon from transporters
\\{br}• Can only be produced once Leighton has reached level 4
   \{/tooltipmedium}
   \{tooltiplong}
The Flamethrower is most effective when used against infantry or buildings. Buildings exposed to the flames start to burn. \\{br}
Flamethrowers can see slightly farther than they can fire, but still have a long range. All enemy and neutral \{ref H_general.seml#_units} units\{/ref} in the line of fire are damaged.
Flamethrowers are produced in the \{ref H_hu_gebaeude.seml#_hu_weapons_smith}Weapon smith\{/ref}.
   \{/tooltiplong}
\{/helpitem}


\{chapter -name _animal_units Animal units}
\{helpitem -name _hu_scout Scout}
\{img /bunit:hu_scout -ralign}
   \{tooltipshort}
%/class:anml/vschtr:+/vsanml:+/vsvhcl:-/vsship:-/vsbldg:--%
   \{/tooltipshort}
   \{tooltipmedium}
• Weak mounted unit
\\{br}• Fast
\\{br}• Excellent vision
   \{/tooltipmedium}
