\{helpitem -name _hu_chariot Chariot}
\{img /bunit:hu_chariot -ralign}
   \{tooltipshort}
%/class:anml/vschtr:+/vsanml:+/vsvhcl:+/vsship:+/vsbldg:--%
   \{/tooltipshort}
   \{tooltipmedium}
   • Weak mounted unit
\\{br}• Fast
\\{br}• May transport 1 infantry unit
   \{/tooltipmedium}
   \{tooltiplong}
