With an \{ref H_hu_produkte.seml#_hu_archer} Archer\{/ref} aboard this \{ref H_general.seml#_units}unit\{/ref} is perfectly suited to hit and run tactics. When embroiled in close combat the stag uses his horns to defend himself. Chariots are produced on the \{ref H_hu_gebaeude.seml#_hu_small_farm} Small animal farm.\{/ref}
   \{/tooltiplong}
\{/helpitem}

\{helpitem -name _hu_wild_boar Wild boar}
\{img /bunit:hu_wild_boar -ralign}
   \{tooltipshort}
