   \{tooltipshort}
%/class:anml/vschtr:+/vsanml:+/vsvhcl:+/vsship:--/vsbldg:--%
   \{/tooltipshort}
   \{tooltipmedium}
• Flying scout unit
\\{br}• Ranged weapon
   \{/tooltipmedium}
   \{tooltiplong}
Produced in \{ref H_hu_gebaeude.seml#_hu_small_farm} Small animal farm \{/ref}, the Pteranodon rider is a cheap and suitable \{ref H_general.seml#_units} unit\{/ref} to do scouting and harassing workers or other units which can't shoot back.\\{br}
   \{/tooltiplong}
\{/helpitem}

\{helpitem -name _hu_rhino Battle rhino}
